TEXT -104 408 Left 2 !*Delay calulation spice code\n*modify this code according to you\n \n\n.meas time1 FIND time WHEN V(Vin) = 1  RISE=1\n.meas time2 FIND time WHEN V(Vout) = 1  FALL=1\n.meas tPHL param time2-time1\n \n.meas time3 FIND time WHEN V(Vin) =  1 FALL=1\n.meas time4 FIND time WHEN V(Vout) = 1 RISE=1\n.meas tPLH param time4-time3\n \n.meas delay param (tPHL+tPLH)/2
